## 핵심 명령어

### 모델 생성
```bash
rails generate model Brand name:string logo:string description:text founded_year:integer country:string category:string
rails generate model Model name:string brand:references year:integer category:string price:decimal engine_displacement:integer weight:decimal fuel_type:string
```

### 컨트롤러 생성
```bash
rails generate controller Brands index show
rails generate controller Models index show
```

### 마이그레이션 및 시드
```bash
rails db:migrate
rails db:seed
```

### 배포
```bash
heroku create mybikes-mvp
git add .
git commit -m "MVP 완성"
git push heroku main
heroku run rails db:migrate
```

